## Findings Summary
- AI-DLC shifts from AI as an assistant to AI as the orchestrator.
- Key Artefacts: Intent (purpose), Unit (cohesive work), Bolt (smallest rapid iteration).
- Rituals: Mob Elaboration (collaborative review of AI outputs).
- Phased Approach: Inception -> Construction -> Operations.
- Brown-field: Context building through elevation into semantic models.
- Human role: "Loss function" (validation, refinement, approval).
